gov.medicaid.controllers.admin

Class SystemAdminUserSearchController

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.medicaid.controllers.admin.BaseSystemAdminController
      • gov.medicaid.controllers.admin.SystemAdminUserSearchController

  • @RequestMapping(value="/system/search/*")
public class SystemAdminUserSearchController
extends BaseSystemAdminController
    This controller class that provides for user search - simple and advanced. Changes in 1.1: add private method getRolesStr and update search to use getRolesStr to get all the roles as an string.

    Thread Safety This class is mutable and not thread safe, but used in thread safe manner by framework.

    Since:
    1.0
    Endpoint:
    "/system/search/*"
